Hmm.  @rstudio graphics device has a bug

Drawing line from (0, 0) to (1, 1) works OK, but getting those coordinates back is completely borked!  i.e. should get back (0, 0) & (1, 1)

Plenty of related bugs on the tracker: https://t.co/mENYNm6uz1

#RStats https://t.co/5Zvh3WCz7J

@rstudio Posted code in support of github issue : https://t.co/6L73HY2ek8

#RStats

And here's how you have to offset and scale coordinates returned by 'grid.locator()' in order for them to work with the @RStudio graphics device.

x <- x * 4/3
